<h1>Dice Game</h1>
<h2>Welcome</h2>
<p>Here are the rules:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Roll the dice to start the game.</li>
	<li>If your first roll is a 7 or 11, you win.</li>
	<li>If your first roll is a 2, 3, or 12, you lose.</li>
	<li>Anything else becomes your <em>point</em>. Roll your point again before a 7 and you win.</li>
</ul>
<%= link_to "Click here to begin the game!", roll_path %>
